posting_body: ['Call Isaac @ 608-622-4508 for a showing', '$1765.00 / Month', '---------------------------', '---------------------------', 'Property Details:', '1 BEDROOMS | 1 BATHROOMS', 'Situated in the heart of Logan Square, where Milwaukee meets California, you’ll find various dining and bar options right outside your doorstep.', 'With the CTA Blue line located a short walk away, you’ll easily access anywhere in downtown Chicago, in addition to O’Hare International airport.', 'Located on tree-lined boulevards, these luxury apartments feature sleek and airy open concept kitchens with stainless steel appliances, plank flooring, in-unit W/D, and floor-to-ceiling windows with sweeping city views.', 'Convenient building amenities include a state-of-the-art fitness center and resident lounge.', 'Four-legged companions are welcome, although some breed and weight restrictions apply.', 'Parking is available at an additional fee.', '***Cats, Small Dogs, Large Dogs Allowed***', 'Property Type:', 'Single Family', 'Lease Terms:', '$1765.00/Month', '$450.00 Deposit', 'Lease Length:', 'One Year', 'Available:', '09/10/2022', 'Unit Amenities:', 'Dishwasher', 'Dryer', 'Freezer', 'Oven', 'Microwave', 'Refrigerator', 'Washer', 'Garbage Disposal', 'Building Amenities:', 'Off Street Parking', 'Security Cameras', 'Secure Building', 'Intercom', 'Fitness Center', 'Bicycle Parking', 'Wired For Internet', '---------------------------', 'Isaac Jones', '608-622-4508', 'HotSpot Rentals(License #481.011892)', 'Check out our 1000 5 Star Reviews', '<URL>', '.']
